<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Course Purchase Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
        }
        .order-details {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .order-details div {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .order-details span {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Course Purchase Confirmation</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= order.userId %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for purchasing the course! We are excited to confirm that we have received your order for the course.</p>

        <div class="order-details">
            <div><span>Order ID:</span> <%= order._id %></div>
            <div><span>Course Name:</span> <%= order.name %></div>
            <div><span>Price:</span> $<%= order.price %></div>
            <div><span>Order Date:</span> <%= order.data %></div>
        </div>

        <p>We will begin processing your access to the course shortly. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us.</p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing AJUS!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>AJUS.EDU | Banglaur, India | ajus.edu@gmail.com</p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
